  "validation_notes": "--project-transport-plan, --segment-start, and --segment-end are required. Status cannot be active without a tractor. Segment start and end must belong to the same project transport plan and start position must be <= end position. All segments in the range must have truckers, and the tractor (if provided) must belong to the same trucker as every segment in the range. Tractor assignments cannot overlap in the same plan. Actualizer window end must be >= start when both are set. A tractor can have only one open actualizer window and actualizer windows cannot overlap.",
